This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection models. The paper also discusses adversarial attacks, which may place it in the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category. Finally, the use of semantic information may suggest that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
